    <h1>Controls Guide</h1>
<p>
<b>
	M1 - Light Attack
	 <br>
	Jump + M1 - Air Counter
	 <br>
	 M2 - Heavy Attack
	 <br>
	Jump + M2 - Guard Break
	 <br>
	F - Block
	 <br>
	 Q - Dash
	 <br>
	Ctrl - Crouch
	 <br>
	M - Menu
	 <br>
	Space - Jump
	 <br>
	Space + Space - Double Jump
	 <br>
	Left Alt - Nen Wheel
</b>
